Use the standard library
This is how to same_chars of s0 and s1:
   Remember that u0 is unique_chars of s0
   Remember that u1 is unique_chars of s1
   Remember that n0 is u0's length
   Remember that n1 is u1's length
   When n0 is not n1, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n0 times:
      Remember that c is item i in u0
      When c is not in u1, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is 1
Now you know